title: Umm Salal | QSL
snippet: Umm Salal Sports Club was founded in 1979 under the name of Al Tadamun Sports Club. The name was changed to Umm Salal in 2004 due to the club’s location. Nicknamed the Barzan’s Falcons and The Orange Fortress, Umm Salal made their debut in the Qatar League in the 2006-07 season.
